Items.c: <[>原來這金只是輔,這土才是主！因為五行相生,這土能生金,能使金更加威力強大！<]>
Items.mt: <[>So this gold is only the auxiliary, this earth is the main! Because the five elements live together, this earth can produce gold, which can make gold more powerful! <]>
